'''的黎波里之战'''（{{lang-ar|معركة طرابلس}} maʼarikat Ṭarābulus）是[[2011年利比亚内战|2011年利比亚内战]]的一大战役，反对派武装于8月20日开始进攻利比亚首都[[的黎波里|的黎波里]]，以实现最终推翻[[卡扎菲|卡扎菲]]统治地位的目标，最終於8月28日完全佔領該城。

由于该市有“美人鱼”之称，所以反对派将此次战役命名为“美人鱼黎明行动”。之所以选择在8月20日进攻首都，反对派领导人表示这是为了纪念公元630年“{{link-en|征服麦加|Conquest of Mecca}}”（[[伊斯兰教|伊斯兰教]]的创始人[[穆罕默德|穆罕默德]]于630年1月带领一万人向[[麦加|麦加]]进发，后来他们和平地佔領麦加）的历史周年日。<ref>Laub, Karin (21 August 2011). [https://www.ajc.com/news/nation-world/libyan-rebels-say-they-1125496.html "Libyan Rebels Say They Are Closing In on Tripoli"]. [[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] (via ''[[The_Atlanta_Journal-Constitution|The Atlanta Journal-Constitution]]''). Retrieved 21 August 2011.</ref>

== 战前形势 ==
在2011年2月时，的黎波里就发生过比较大的冲突，当时抗议者在[[绿色广场|绿色广场]]（目前已改名为烈士广场）进行集会。而在该市东部的{{link-en|塔久拉|Tajura}}地区反政府的力量也很大，不过一直被卡扎菲部队所压制着。

接下来的几个月的时间里，在首都的抗议也时有发生。而在夜间，一些居民也在街上与政府军做[[游击战|游击战]]，甚至据反对派武装成员说，在支持反对派的地区不少小的街道已被他们占领。<ref>Golovnina, Maria (11 April 2011). [http://uk.reuters.com/article/2011/04/11/libya-guerrilla-idUKLDE73A15F20110411?sp=true "Feature–Rebels Resort to Guerrilla Tactics in Western Libya"] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/5xs1mNh3r?url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/2011/04/11/libya-guerrilla-idUKLDE73A15F20110411?sp=true |date=20110411175713 |dateformat=iso }}. [[Reuters|Reuters]]. Retrieved 21 August 2011.</ref>

从8月13日开始，来自[[奈富塞山|奈富塞山]]（Nafusa Mountains）的一支部隊接近首都的沿海地区。在经过战斗后，西部的[[索曼|索曼]]（Sorman）、[[塞卜拉泰|塞卜拉泰]]以及[[扎维耶|扎维耶]]被他们占领，并切断了政府军连接突尼斯的通道和补给线，还孤立了[[祖瓦拉|祖瓦拉]]。同时在南边，另一路反对派武装占领了奈富塞山的门户[[盖尔扬|盖尔扬]]，切断了首都与政府军控制的南部城市[[塞卜哈|塞卜哈]]的通道。紧着是他们又占领了首都东边的[[兹利坦|兹利坦]]，这样就孤立了政府军控制的[[塔瓦哈|塔瓦哈]]（Taworgha，位于兹利坦和米苏拉塔之间）。在反对派取得西路，南部和东路三条陆路的控制权后，即形成反对派武装围攻首都的态势。8月16日，在北约空中力量的帮助下，反对派已经对的黎波里周边的一些关键城镇持续了两天的进攻并占领重要据点，并在南部和西部对首都展开包围之势。他们也开始切断首都的燃料补给线，为接下来的围攻做准备。

== 战役经过 ==
=== 8月19日 ===
反对派武装与北约事前已经协调好进攻计划。而在当晚，反对派用[[拖船|拖船]]将武器偷运到首都。<ref>Lopez, Dario (21 August 2011).  [http://www.3news.co.nz/Heavy-gunfire-in-Tripoli-as-rebels-close-in/tabid/417/articleID/222904/Default.aspx "Heavy Gunfire in Tripoli as Rebels Close In"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.3news.co.nz/Heavy-gunfire-in-Tripoli-as-rebels-close-in/tabid/417/articleID/222904/Default.aspx |date=20121005035914 }}. [[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] (via [[TV3_(New_Zealand)|TV3 News]]). Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>

=== 8月20日 ===
位于[[扎维耶|扎维耶]]的反对派武装对一座距首都仅有27公里的桥梁展开争夺战，并计划于21日进攻首都。<ref>[http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-21-2011-0017 Libya – 21 Aug 2011 – 00:17] {{Wayback|url=http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-21-2011-0017 |date=20120131083522 }}. [[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]]. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>

当晚，随着从市内一座清真寺发出的广播引爆了穆斯林民众的起义。<ref>Ryan, Missy (22 August 2011). [http://in.reuters.com/article/2011/08/22/idINIndia-58893220110822 "Gaddafi Tanks Emerge After Rebels Sweep into Tripoli"] {{Wayback|url=http://in.reuters.com/article/2011/08/22/idINIndia-58893220110822 |date=20111212140609 }}.  [[Reuters|Reuters]].  Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>起义的核心地带位于市区的本·纳比清真寺（Ben Nabi Mosque）。当时年轻人在那里聚集，祷告活动被取消，妇女被送回家。当人们使用扩音器开始广播高喊反对卡扎菲的口号后，政府军抵达后开始袭击清真寺，但是被躲藏在国家电视台附近的武装民众打退。<ref>Reevell, James. (31 May 2011) [http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/libya/8714522/Libya-how-Operation-Mermaid-Dawn-the-move-to-take-Tripoli-unfolded.html "Libya: How 'Operation Mermaid Dawn', The Move To Take Tripoli, Unfolded"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/libya/8714522/Libya-how-Operation-Mermaid-Dawn-the-move-to-take-Tripoli-unfolded.html |date=20110822030054 }}. ''[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]''. Retrieved 21 August 2011.</ref>首都的居民在道路上设置路障并燃烧轮胎，为反对派提供支持。起义很快传遍首都许多地区，如首都周边的法什卢姆（Fashloum）、朱馬市場區（Souq al-Juma）、塔久拉和本阿什（Ben Ashur），就这样首都各地都打响了反对卡扎菲的战斗。<ref>Staff (21 August 2011). [http://edition.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/africa/08/20/libya.war/index.html "Gadhafi Defiant as Rebels Claim To Take 'Revolution' Inside Tripoli"] {{Wayback|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/africa/08/20/libya.war/index.html |date=20110822201101 }}. [[CNN|CNN]]. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>当晚比较激烈的战斗发生在郊区朱馬市場區和阿拉达（Arrada）大街。<ref>Lamloum, Imed (21 August 2011).  [http://news.smh.com.au/breaking-news-world/fighting-erupts-in-tripoli-20110821-1j4b5.html "Libya Rebels Close In on Tripoli"]. [[Agence_France-Presse|Agence France-Presse]] (via ''[[The_Sydney_Morning_Herald|The Sydney Morning Herald]]''). Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>反卡扎菲的居民也封锁了阿尔斯卡（Alsika）大街。

当晚反对派也占领了首都的[[的黎波里国际机场|国际机场]]和军火库。<ref>Staff (21 August 2011).  [http://news.xinhuanet.com/english2010/world/2011-08/21/c_131063416.htm "Libyan Rebels Capture Weapons Depot in Capital"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english2010/world/2011-08/21/c_131063416.htm |date=20121108021850 }}. [[Xinhua_News_Agency|Xinhua News Agency]].  Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>居民则收到了政府发出的要求他们与反对派战斗的信息。<ref>Lowe, Christian (20 August 2011). [http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/20/libya-tripoli-protests-idUSLDE77J04W20110820 "Anti-Gaddafi Protests in Tripoli Streets:Residents"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/20/libya-tripoli-protests-idUSLDE77J04W20110820 |date=20120726045433 }}. [[Reuters|Reuters]]. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>记者们也听到了该市发出的密集的爆炸和交火的声音。<ref>Staff (20 August 2011). [http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14605391 "Libya Conflict: Heavy Gunfire Erupts in Tripoli"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14605391 |date=20110821030200 }}. [[BBC_News|BBC News]].  Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>

不过，卡扎菲政府发言人向记者表示首都是安全的，政府军已经消灭了“一小搓叛乱分子”，并仍然控制着该市。<ref>Staff (20 August 2011). [http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2011/08/20/heavy-clashes-marked-by-gunfire-screams-break-out-in-area-of-tripoli/ "Live Blog: Clashes Reported as Rebels Claim To Take Right into Tripoli"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2011/08/20/heavy-clashes-marked-by-gunfire-screams-break-out-in-area-of-tripoli/ |date=20120902130920 }}. [[CNN|CNN]]. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref><ref name=autogenerated2>Lopez, Dario (21 August 2011). [http://www.3news.co.nz/Heavy-gunfire-in-Tripoli-as-rebels-close-in/tabid/417/articleID/222904/Default.aspx "Heavy Gunfire in Tripoli as Rebels Close In"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.3news.co.nz/Heavy-gunfire-in-Tripoli-as-rebels-close-in/tabid/417/articleID/222904/Default.aspx |date=20121005035914 }} [[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] (via [[TV3_(New_Zealand)|TV3 News]]).  Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>

=== 8月21日 ===
来自[[扎维耶|扎维耶]]的反对派武装向东朝着首都进发。他们到达扎维耶东部的Jadda'im镇后，仅遇到了很少的政府军的抵抗就占领该地。<ref name="bare_url">[http://news.sky.com/home/world-news/article/16053951 Tripoli, Libya: Rebels Close In On Colonel Gaddafi And Central Tripoli Meeting Almost No Resistance] {{Wayback|url=http://news.sky.com/home/world-news/article/16053951 |date=20110823164645 }}. [[Sky_News|Sky News]]. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref><ref>[http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/2011/08/21/libyan-rebels-only-miles-from-tripoli-as-mad-dog-gaddafi-is-cornered-86908-23361562/ Libyan rebels only miles from Tripoli as Mad Dog Gaddafi is cornered] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/2011/08/21/libyan-rebels-only-miles-from-tripoli-as-mad-dog-gaddafi-is-cornered-86908-23361562/ |date=20110913152636 }}. ''The Daily Record''. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>接下来他们又占领了首都西部的马亚镇。<ref>[http://english.aljazeera.net/news/africa/2011/08/201182193129278233.html Libyan rebels in 'final push' for capital – Africa] {{Wayback|url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/africa/2011/08/201182193129278233.html |date=20110828232424 }}. [[Al_Jazeera_English|Al Jazeera English]]. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>

21日早晨，来自[[米苏拉塔|米苏拉塔]]和[[兹利坦|兹利坦]]的船满载着反对派武装和武器抵达首都港口，开始参加战斗。<ref>[http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-21-2011-1822 Libya live blog 21 August] {{Wayback|url=http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-21-2011-1822 |date=20110825151506 }}. [[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]]. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>

[[半岛电视台|半岛电视台]]报道当天早上战斗一直在持续着。有许多反对派武装成员在包围卡迪（Qadah）地区的米提加空军基地时被打死。<ref>[http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2011/08/21/163268.html Qaddafi scorns rebel ‘rats’ as fighting breaks out in besieged Tripoli] {{Wayback|url=http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2011/08/21/163268.html |date=20110822075308 }}. English.alarabiya.net (18 August 2011). Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref><ref>[http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-21-2011-0134 Libya – 21 Aug 2011 – 01:34 ] {{Wayback|url=http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-21-2011-0134 |date=20110825052305 }}. [[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]]. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>塔久拉地区全部被反对派占领，而朱馬市場區、Arada地区以及米提加空军基地的战斗则一直持续着。<ref>[http://af.reuters.com/article/libyaNews/idAFLDE77J06920110820 UPDATE 1-Libyan rebels fight for Tripoli airbase -activist] {{Wayback|url=http://af.reuters.com/article/libyaNews/idAFLDE77J06920110820 |date=20120725203734 }}. [[Reuters|Reuters]] (9 February 2009). Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>在首都西部的卡迪、Zawiyat al Dahmania、法什卢姆和本阿什都发生了激烈的交火<ref name=autogenerated3>[http://www.montrealgazette.com/news/Zero+hour+Gadhafi+besieged+Tripoli+rises/5284367/story.html "Zero hour" for Gadhafi as Tripoli rises up]{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}. ''Montreal Gazette''. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>。一名反对派武装代表在结束了阿齐齐亚的战斗后表示行动“进行得比较轻松”。<ref>[http://edition.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/africa/08/20/libya.war/ Gadhafi defiant as rebels claim to take 'revolution' inside Tripoli] {{Wayback|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/africa/08/20/libya.war/ |date=20121025125155 }}. [[CNN|CNN]]. Retrieved [22 August 2011.</ref>

一名来自塔久拉地区的居民告诉半岛电视台的记者说，当地居民打退卡扎菲的部队控制该地后，他们释放了大约450名健康状况很糟的军事基地里的囚犯，而那些撤退的政府军目前在炮击周边地区。<ref>[http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/Libya Libya Live Blog] {{Wayback|url=http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/Libya |date=20110821025737 }}. [[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]]. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>

截止当天下午，反对派已完全控制塔久拉、Suq al-Jumaa、Arada和埃撒巴（al-Sabaa）这些地区。而在本阿什、法什卢姆和Zawiyat al-Dahmani则在持续战斗着。此外，他们也控制了法什卢姆、Zawiyat al-Dahmani以及曼苏尔（Mansoura）的大部分地区。<ref>[http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-21-2011-1407 Libya – 21 Aug 2011 – 14:07] {{Wayback|url=http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-21-2011-1407 |date=20110824233019 }}. [[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]]. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>他们还占领一个手机运营公司。<ref>[http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-21-2011-1838 al jazeera blog] {{Wayback|url=http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-21-2011-1838 |date=20110824225707 }}. [[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]]. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>

在英国下午时间6:04，BBC报道反对派位于首都以西12公里，<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14606749 BBC live report 1804 entry] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14606749 |date=20110822102046 }}. [[BBC_News|BBC News]]. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>到了6:39又报道他们已经进入首都。<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14606749 BBC live report 1839 entry] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14606749 |date=20110822102046 }}. [[BBC_News|BBC News]]. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>7:02报道说反对派武装抵达郊区詹祖尔（Janzour）并受到当地民众的热烈欢迎。<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14606749 BBC live report 1902 entry] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14606749 |date=20110822102046 }}. [[BBC_News|BBC News]]. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>

晚上来自扎维耶的反对派武装没有遭遇任何抵抗进入郊区詹祖尔，并受到挥舞着革命旗帜的居民的喝彩。<ref>[http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-21-2011-2306 Libya – 21 Aug 2011 – 23:06] {{Wayback|url=http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-21-2011-2306 |date=20110824232519 }}. [[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]]. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sky.com/home/article/16053951|title=Libyan Rebels: 'Colonel Gaddafi's Son Captured'|publisher=Sky|accessdate=2011-08-22|archive-date=2011-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111026150518/http://news.sky.com/home/article/16053951|dead-url=no}}</ref>当晚卡扎菲卫队向反对派武装投降，[[哈米斯旅|哈米斯旅]]的主要头目也被反对派武装解雇。<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14606749 BBC 2146] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14606749 |date=20110822102046 }}. [[BBC_News|BBC News]]. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>有居民表示，在反对派武装进入首都后，一些居民加入到了欢庆的队伍中。<ref name="bare_url" />

卡扎菲政府发言人称，估计在当晚首都战斗中有1300人死亡，5000人受伤。<ref>[http://www.theatlanticwire.com/global/2011/08/qaddafis-last-stand/41530/ Qaddafi's Last Stand: A Live Blog – Global] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theatlanticwire.com/global/2011/08/qaddafis-last-stand/41530/ |date=20110915011156 }}. The Atlantic Wire. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>

==== 俘获卡扎菲的儿子 ====
===== 长子 =====
半岛电视台报道说卡扎菲的大儿子[[穆罕默德·格達費|穆罕默德·卡扎菲]]被俘虏。<ref>[http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-22-2011-0104 Libya – 22 Aug 2011 – 01:04] {{Wayback|url=http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-22-2011-0104 |date=20110825073756 }}. Al Jazeera Blogs. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref><ref>[http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-22-2011-0348 Libya – 22 Aug 2011 – 03:48] {{Wayback|url=http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-22-2011-0348 |date=20110825005118 }}. Al Jazeera Blogs. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>该台在采访穆罕默德·卡扎菲时，他显示出道歉的态度，但谴责说暴力革命是缺乏智慧的做法。<ref>[http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-22-2011-0335 Libya – 22 Aug 2011 – 03:35] {{Wayback|url=http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-22-2011-0335 |date=20110825020817 }}. Al Jazeera Blogs. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>之前，曾有利比亚反对派官员称卡扎菲长子穆罕默德·卡扎菲是向反对派投降的。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2011-08-22/065623028862.shtml|title=利比亚反对派称卡扎菲长子穆罕默德已投降|publisher=[[新华网|新华网]]|language=zh-hans|date=2011年8月22日|accessdate=2011-08-23|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304105516/http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2011-08-22/065623028862.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>之后，又被政府军救出。

===== 次子 =====
[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]和[[半岛电视台|半岛电视台]]报道反对派武装抵达市中心的烈士广场，过渡委员会主席说卡扎菲二子[[赛义夫·伊斯拉姆·卡扎菲|赛义夫·伊斯拉姆·卡扎菲]]已被俘虏。<ref>[http://www.iol.co.za/news/africa/gaddafi-s-sons-arrested-report-1.1122085?showComments=true Gaddafi’s sons arrested – report – Africa | IOL News] {{Wayback|url=http://www.iol.co.za/news/africa/gaddafi-s-sons-arrested-report-1.1122085?showComments=true |date=20120820032114 }}. IOL.co.za (5 May 2010). Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]报道阿齐齐亚兵营已经被包围。<ref>Katrandjian, Olivia. (21 July 2011) [http://abcnews.go.com/International/libyan-rebels-captured-gadhafis-son-tripoli/story?id=14349513 Libyan Rebels Say They Have Captured Two of Gadhafi's Sons in Tripoli] {{Wayback|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/libyan-rebels-captured-gadhafis-son-tripoli/story?id=14349513 |date=20110822045509 }}.  [[ABC_News|ABC News]]. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Al Jazeera TV News|agency=[[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera TV]]|location=[[Qatar|Qatar]]|language=ar|accessdate=21 August 2011 at 09:00 pm UTC}}</ref>[[天空新闻台|天空新闻台]]报道说英国驻班加西大使证实了赛义夫被俘的事实，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://twitter.com/#!/JohnRentoul/status/105385240851267584 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-08-22 |archive-date=2016-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161103181657/https://twitter.com/notch/status/192755231275229185#!/JohnRentoul/status/105385240851267584 |dead-url=no }}</ref>过渡委员会表示会确保赛义夫的安全以便以后接受司法审判。<ref>[http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2011/08/22/163423.html Qaddafi plea: 'Save Libya,' after son's capture; may negotiate with rebel council] {{Wayback|url=http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2011/08/22/163423.html |date=20110822080757 }}. English.alarabiya.net. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>[[国际刑事法院|国际刑事法院]]也证实了该消息，并表示他们会向过渡委员会请求移交赛义夫给他们以让他接受所指控的反人类罪的国际法院的审判。<ref>[http://news.nationalpost.com/2011/08/21/libyan-rebels-take-tripolis-green-square Libyan rebels take Tripoli’s Green Square]. ''[[National_Post|National Post]]''. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref><ref>[http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/muammar-gaddafis-son-has-been-arrested-and-will-face-charges-of-crimes-against-humanity/story-e6frg6so-1226119478596 Muammar Gaddafi's son has been arrested, and will face charges of crimes against humanity]. ''The Australian'' (21 February 2011). Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>

然而，卡扎菲的次子赛义夫·伊斯兰·卡扎菲8月23日凌晨在利比亚首都的黎波里阿齐齐亚兵营举行记者会，宣布有关他被反对派武装抓捕的消息是谎言。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2011-08/23/c_121898211.htm|title=卡扎菲次子赛义夫否认被抓传言|publisher=[[新华网|新华网]]|language=zh-hans|date=2011年8月23日|accessdate=2011年8月23日|archive-date=2014年4月22日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422173959/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2011-08/23/c_121898211.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===== 三子 =====
阿拉伯电视台的记者引用过渡委员会的说法报道三子[[薩阿迪·格達費|薩阿迪·格達費]]已经被反对派俘虏，他是于21日被俘的，具体地点不确定。

=== 8月22日 ===
截止当地时间凌晨一点，反对派武装表示已经控制首都90℅的地区，包括市中心的广场。<ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2028415/Libya-Rebels-capture-military-base-near-Tripoli-warn-zero-hour-Gaddafi.html Libya: Tripoli captured by rebels as Colonel Gaddafi's son Saif arrested]. ''Daily Mail''. (18 August 2011). Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>英国广播公司和半岛电视台都证实反对派武装进入广场的事实。<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14606749 As it happened: Libya conflict] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14606749 |date=20110822102046 }}. BBC News. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref><ref>[http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-22-2011-0300-0 Libya – 22 Aug 2011 – 03:00]. Al Jazeera Blogs. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>

当地时间1:15，过渡委员会宣布他们已经控制首都的国际机场和南部地区。<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14610722 Libya conflict] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14610722 |date=20160202134932 }}. BBC News. Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref>早晨，一名反对派武装高级指挥官表示，在首都仍然有效忠卡扎菲的残余部队，他要求警察坚守岗位作好防范工作。<ref>http://www.vancouversun.com/news/thewest/Libyan+rebel+leader+says+pockets+resistance+still+exist+Tripoli/5286702/story.html{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

上午，法国媒体报道，在卡扎菲住所的附近和首都南部有战斗发生。反对派武装指挥官说卡扎菲部队仍控制着该市15℅到20℅的地区。而在卡扎菲住所的附近，出现了多辆坦克开始炮击首都的一些地区。<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14610722] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14610722 |date=20160202134932 }}.  [[BBC_News|BBC News]].  Retrieved 22 August 2011.</ref><ref name="mercurynews">http://www.mercurynews.com/nation-world/ci_18730975</ref>在卡扎菲势力控制的外国记者下榻的瑞克索斯饭店（Rixos Hotel）附近有激烈的交火，<ref name="mercurynews" />记者被政府军禁止离开酒店，于是记者描述为他们这些记者是被政府军利用做掩护和盾牌。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://world.huanqiu.com/roll/2011-08/1938096.html |language= |title=美媒称的黎波里外国记者宾馆形同“监狱” |publisher=环球网 |date=2011年8月23日 |accessdate= |archive-date=2012年1月6日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120106202038/http://world.huanqiu.com/roll/2011-08/1938096.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>http://news.ninemsn.com.au/world/8288763/journalists-trapped-inside-tripoli-hotel {{Wayback|url=http://news.ninemsn.com.au/world/8288763/journalists-trapped-inside-tripoli-hotel |date=20121007025728 }} Accessed August 22, 2011</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/23/8614868_0.shtml |language= |title=30多名国际记者被困利比亚 凤凰卫视发表五点声明 |publisher=凤凰卫视 |date=2011年8月23日 |accessdate= |archive-date=2011年8月23日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110823123802/http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/23/8614868_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>上午8:32，有报道说卡扎菲还留在[[阿齐齐亚兵营|阿齐齐亚兵营]]里，周围有重型武器保卫着他。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4112204,00.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-08-22 |archive-date=2012-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120823071204/http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4112204,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/22/8592633_0.shtml |title=的黎波里重要地点地图 |accessdate=2011-08-22 |archive-date=2011-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110823121950/http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/22/8592633_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

有数百名反对派武装成员往烈士广场搬运[[火箭炮|火箭炮]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://af.reuters.com/article/libyaNews/idAFLDE77L08W20110822 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-08-22 |archive-date=2012-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120725182413/http://af.reuters.com/article/libyaNews/idAFLDE77L08W20110822 |dead-url=no }}</ref>而在卡扎菲所在地以及港口附近仍进行着战斗，效忠卡扎菲的部队用坦克进行着防御。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://af.reuters.com/article/libyaNews/idAFLDE77L0B320110822 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-08-22 |archive-date=2012-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120725183603/http://af.reuters.com/article/libyaNews/idAFLDE77L0B320110822 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

英国广播公司报道证实反对派已经控制国家电视台大楼。<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14610722] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14610722 |date=20160202134932 }}. [[BBC_News|BBC News]].</ref>卡扎菲部队控制着阿齐齐亚兵营、瑞克索斯饭店、位于塔久拉地区的一家医院<ref>{{citation | url = http://www.upi.com/Top_News/World-News/2011/08/22/Rebels-control-great-majority-of-Tripoli/UPI-80251313996400?dailybrief | title = Rebels control great majority of Tripoli | publisher = [[United_Press_International|United Press International]] | date = 2011-08-22 | accessdate = 2011-08-23 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304063555/http://www.upi.com/Top_News/World-News/2011/08/22/Rebels-control-great-majority-of-Tripoli/UPI-80251313996400?dailybrief | dead-url = no }}.</ref>, 以及部分港口<ref>{{citation | url = http://www.tv3.ie/article.php?article_id=61945&locID=1.2&pagename=news | title = News | publisher = [[TV3|TV3]] | place = IE | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120717040415/http://www.tv3.ie/article.php?article_id=61945&locID=1.2&pagename=news | archivedate = 2012-07-17 }}.</ref>。而米提加空军基地的状况不是很清楚，虽然有许多报道说反对派已经控制该地。<ref>{{citation | url = http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-21/libya-rebels-battle-qaddafi-troops-in-tripoli-say-they-hold-neighborhoods.html | title = Libya rebels battle Quaddafi troops in Tripoli, say they hold neighborhoods | publisher = [[Bloomberg_L.P.|Bloomberg]] | date = 2011-08-21 | accessdate = 2011-08-23 | archive-date = 2014-07-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140709010301/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-21/libya-rebels-battle-qaddafi-troops-in-tripoli-say-they-hold-neighborhoods.html | dead-url = no }}.</ref>

整个下午，反对派陆续从烈士广场撤退，因为他们计划向别处进发。塔久拉地区的反对派说他们在与固守在一家医院里的卡扎菲部队进行谈判劝降工作。<ref>[http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/africa/08/22/libya.war/index.html "Gadhafi Regime 'Crumbling' as Rebels Battle for Tripoli"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/africa/08/22/libya.war/index.html |date=20121110130000 }}. [[CNN|CNN]].</ref>

晚上，首都西部的反对派被打退。<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14611549 "Libya Conflict: Fighting Rages Near Gaddafi Compound"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14611549 |date=20110823012827 }}. [[BBC_News|BBC News]].</ref>此外，有报道暗示卡扎菲正试图通过残余部队的帮助逃离其所在地。<ref>[http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-22-2011-2122 ''Libya Live Blog'': Monday, August 22, 2011&nbsp– 18:22"] {{Wayback|url=http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-22-2011-2122 |date=20120131093218 }}. [[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]].</ref>夜晚，一名反对派成员说他估计将与卡扎菲部队有一场硬仗要打，而反对派也正在首都的各大路口设置检查点以避免卡扎菲逃跑。<ref>{{citation | url = http://af.reuters.com/article/libyaNews/idAFLDE77L0UE20110822 | publisher = [[Reuters|Reuters]] | title = Libya news | accessdate = 2011-08-23 | archive-date = 2016-03-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303224809/http://af.reuters.com/article/libyaNews/idAFLDE77L0UE20110822 | dead-url = no }}.</ref>

米苏拉塔的反对派地方军事委员会说，他们已经派出“携带有大量战士和武器”的几艘船只到首都做援助，而此前一天的21日，他们也曾派200名士兵抵达塔久拉。<ref>[http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/Libya] {{Wayback|url=http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/Libya |date=20110821025737 }}. [[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]].</ref>

=== 8月23日 ===
早晨，[[CNN|CNN]]记者[[馬修·錢斯|馬修·錢斯]]报道说，他看到了[[赛义夫·伊斯拉姆·卡扎菲|赛义夫·伊斯拉姆·卡扎菲]]在护卫队陪伴下出现在了瑞克索斯饭店（Rixos Hotel）附近。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2011/08/22/live-blog-battle-for-libya-gadhafi-stronghold-under-assault/?hpt=hp_t1 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-08-23 |archive-date=2016-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160208035602/http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2011/08/22/live-blog-battle-for-libya-gadhafi-stronghold-under-assault/?hpt=hp_t1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>阿拉伯电视台报道说被俘的赛义夫后来逃跑了。<ref>{{citation | publisher = Twitter | newspaper = Al Arabiya | url = https://twitter.com/#!/AlArabiya_Brk/status/105812507427475458 | title = Status | accessdate = 2011-08-22 | archive-date = 2016-11-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161103181657/https://twitter.com/notch/status/192755231275229185#!/AlArabiya_Brk/status/105812507427475458 | dead-url = no }}.</ref><ref>{{citation | url = http://english.aljazeera.net/indepth/spotlight/libya/2011/08/2011822235934828611.html | date = 2011-08-22 | publisher = Al Jazeera | title = In Depth: spotlight Libya | accessdate = 2011-08-23 | archive-date = 2011-10-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111006073029/http://english.aljazeera.net/indepth/spotlight/libya/2011/08/2011822235934828611.html | dead-url = no }}.</ref>

下午，半岛电视台记者柯德尔（Zeina Khodr）报道说，她听到曼苏尔地区发生激烈交火，而反对派武装距离阿齐齐亚兵营只剩500米。<ref name="bare_url_a">{{dead link|date=August 2011|reason=link is to dynamic page}} [http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/Libya] {{Wayback|url=http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/Libya |date=20110821025737 }}. [[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]].</ref>

此后在阿齐齐亚兵营的战斗很快打响。《[[卫报|卫报]]》描述大爆炸、[[火箭炮|火箭炮]]和[[机枪|机枪]]等各种火拼激烈进行着。双方分别动用了[[榴弹炮|榴弹炮]]、[[重机枪|重机枪]]和高射机枪对射，激战持续了5个多小时。<ref>{{dead link|date=August 2011|reason=link is to dynamic page. will be stale in 24 or so hours.}} [http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/middle-east-live/2011/aug/23/libya-battle-for-tripoli-live-blog?utm_source=twitterfeed&utm_medium=twitter#block-6]. ''[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]''.</ref>下午晚些时候，反对派开始攻破兵营的一个大门<ref name="bare_url_a" />。尽管卡扎菲部队试图抵抗，但最终有的被打死有的逃离，反对派涌入后朝空中开火庆祝。<ref>{{dead link|date=August 2011|reason=link is to dynamic page}} [http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/middle-east-live/2011/aug/23/libya-tripoli-battle-live-updates#block-43] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/middle-east-live/2011/aug/23/libya-tripoli-battle-live-updates#block-43 |date=20110823190512 }}. ''[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]''.</ref><ref>Staff (23 August 2011). [http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-23-2011-1819 "''Libya Live Blog'': Tuesday, August 23, 2011 – 16:19]. [[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]]. Retrieved 23 August 2011.</ref><ref name=Reuterscompound>{{dead link|date=August 2011|reason=link is to dynamic page}} {{cite news|title=Breaking news: compound|url=http://live.reuters.com/UK/Event/Tripoli_Besieged|accessdate=23 August 2011| publisher = Reuters|date=23 August 2011}}</ref>

反对派成功攻入兵营后，将三色旗插在了卡扎菲的官邸中，并捣毁卡扎菲的铜制雕像。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/23/8626998_0.shtml |language= |title=利比亚反对派攻入卡扎菲官邸升起旗帜 |publisher=环球网 |date=2011年8月23日 |accessdate= |archive-date=2011年8月24日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110824172322/http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/23/8626998_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/24/8633947_0.shtml |language= |title=利反对派夺取阿齐齐亚兵营 捣毁卡扎菲塑像(组图) |publisher=中国新闻网 |date=2011年8月24日 |accessdate= |archive-date=2011年8月24日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110824154510/http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/24/8633947_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Stanglin, Douglas (23 August 2011). [http://content.usatoday.com/communities/ondeadline/post/2011/08/reports-rebels-enter-gadhafi-compound-raise-flag/1 "Rebels Storm Gadhafi Compound, Raise Flag"] {{Wayback|url=http://content.usatoday.com/communities/ondeadline/post/2011/08/reports-rebels-enter-gadhafi-compound-raise-flag/1 |date=20111011154200 }}. ''[[USA_Today|USA Today]]''. Retrieved 23 August 2011.</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Staff | date = 23 August 2011 | url = http://en.trend.az/regions/met/arabicr/1922142.html | title = Rebels Claim They Entered Gaddafi Compound | publisher = [[Trend_News_Agency|Trend News Agency]] | accessdate =2011-08-23| archive-date = 2011-08-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110826234357/http://en.trend.az/regions/met/arabicr/1922142.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>记者展示反对派缴获了的大批卡扎菲的私人物品，包括他的医疗档案、镀金的[[SVD狙擊步槍|SVD狙擊步槍]]<ref>[http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2011/08/23/live-blog-gadhafi-son-reappears-in-tripoli/?on.cnn=1] {{Wayback|url=http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2011/08/23/live-blog-gadhafi-son-reappears-in-tripoli/?on.cnn=1 |date=20111117145737 }}. [[CNN|CNN]]</ref>、他的帽子和[[高球車|高球車]]（在[[高爾夫球|高爾夫球]]球場使用的一種交通工具）等个人物品。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.163.com/photoview/00AO0001/17210.html#p=7C79DVB500AO0001 |language= |title=利比亚反对派攻陷卡扎菲阿齐齐亚兵营(组图) |publisher=网易新闻 |date=2011-08-24 |accessdate= |archive-date=2011-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111008032608/http://news.163.com/photoview/00AO0001/17210.html#p=7C79DVB500AO0001 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Staff (23 August 2011). [http://news.sky.com/home/world-news/article/16055646 "Rebels Swipe Gaddafi's Hat and Golf Cart"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.sky.com/home/world-news/article/16055646 |date=20110908075252 }}. [[Sky_News|Sky News]]. Retrieved 23 August 2011.</ref>半岛电视台还在19:30直播了兵营内部现场的画面。<ref>{{full|date=August 2011}} {{cite news|title=[[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]] live TV channel|publisher = [[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]] live TV channel|language=ar | accessdate= 23 August 2001 at 16:30 UTC}}</ref>不过现场没有俘获卡扎菲和他的儿子们。<ref>{{cite news | date = 23 August 2011 | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14630702 | title = Rebels Overun Gadhafi Compound | publisher = BBC News | accessdate = 23 August 2011 | archive-date = 2016-02-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160202134932/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14630702 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

而随后卡扎菲发布的一个录音讲话说，他逃离兵营只是“战术转移”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://af.reuters.com/article/libyaNews/idAFL5E7JN29K20110823 |title=Gaddafi says withdraws from Tripoli compound | News by Country | Reuters |publisher=Af.reuters.com |date=2009-02-09 |accessdate=2011-08-24 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303175758/http://af.reuters.com/article/libyaNews/idAFL5E7JN29K20110823 |dead-url=no }}</ref>而据国际象棋联合会主席伊柳姆日诺夫23日说，卡扎菲当天在与他通电话时说自己仍在的黎波里，“健康地活着”，他表示不会离开利比亚。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/23/8626576_0.shtml |language= |title=卡扎菲：我还在的黎波里不会离开利比亚 |publisher=新华网 |date=2011年8月23日 |accessdate= |archive-date=2011年8月27日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110827012600/http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/23/8626576_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

后来，一些卡扎菲残余部队又用枪火攻击聚集在兵营里的人群，当时里面的外国记者开始撤离兵营，一名半岛电视台记者受伤。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/africa/08/23/libya.war/index.html |title='The fall of the capital means the fall of the regime' -- rebel leader |accessdate=2011-08-24 |archive-date=2011-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110823122952/http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/africa/08/23/libya.war/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

晚上，反对派发言人宣布他们可以维护阿布萨利姆（Abu Slim）地区的安全，因为当地人跟卡扎菲家族的关系比较亲密。<ref>Staff (23 August 2011).[http://af.reuters.com/article/libyaNews/idAFL5E7JN28K20110823 "Rebels Seize Pro-Gaddafi Tripoli District – Spokesman"] {{Wayback|url=http://af.reuters.com/article/libyaNews/idAFL5E7JN28K20110823 |date=20120725192733 }}. [[Reuters|Reuters]]. Retrieved 23 August 2011.</ref>

==== 卡扎菲家人的状况 ====
8月22日，卡扎菲所处的地点不是很确定，一般认为他仍在阿齐齐亚兵营里。<ref>[http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4112204,00.html] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4112204,00.html |date=20120823071204 }}. [[Ynetnews|Ynetnews]].</ref>而有一个报道则说他在塔久拉地区的一个医院里，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2011/08/22/163445.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-08-23 |archive-date=2011-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110822105626/http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2011/08/22/163445.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>半岛电视台报道说他在医院里的部队成功地击退了反对派的进攻。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/44224936/ns/world_news-mideast_n_africa/#.TlLXUqiV6yw |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-08-23 |archive-date=2011-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111009105851/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/44224936/ns/world_news-mideast_n_africa/#.TlLXUqiV6yw |dead-url=no }}</ref>五子[[奥-穆·坦塞姆·比拉·卡扎菲|奧-穆·坦塞姆·比拉·格達費]]则仍在阿齐齐亚兵营里指挥着防御战斗，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.emirates247.com/news/world/libyan-pm-escapes-to-tunisia-2011-08-22-1.414541 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-08-23 |archive-date=2012-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120525103247/http://www.emirates247.com/news/world/libyan-pm-escapes-to-tunisia-2011-08-22-1.414541 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english2010/world/2011-08/22/c_131067055.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-08-23 |archive-date=2012-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108024042/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english2010/world/2011-08/22/c_131067055.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>报道说七子[[哈米斯·卡扎菲|哈米斯·格達費]]（此前反对派说他在兹利坦被北约炸死）在首都中心指挥着残余坦克部队进行着反攻，其目的是试图解除对阿齐齐亚兵营的围困。<ref>[http://www.canberratimes.com.au/news/world/world/general/gaddafis-regime-crumbling/2266981.aspx]</ref><ref>[http://www.thefirstpost.co.uk/83419,people,news,three-held-one-fighting-back-tale-of-gaddafis-four-sons-saif-muhammad-and-khamis-in-libya]</ref>

Al Arabiya 的记者引用过渡委员会的说法报道三子[[薩阿迪·格達費|薩阿迪·格達費]]已经被反对派俘虏，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/22/us-libya-saadi-idUSTRE77L3PI20110822 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-08-23 |archive-date=2011-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111020062924/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/22/us-libya-saadi-idUSTRE77L3PI20110822 |dead-url=no }}</ref>他是在此前一天21日被俘的，具体地点和时间还不确定。

22日，在首都发现了两具被烧焦的[[屍體|屍體]]，半岛电视台表示这两具尸体可能是[[哈米斯·卡扎菲|哈米斯·格達費]]和情报部门主管[[阿卜杜拉·塞努西|阿卜杜拉·塞努西]]的，<ref>[http://www.agi.it/english-version/all/elenco-notizie/201108221957-cro-ren1079-bodies_found_in_tripoli_maybe_khamis_gaddafi_and_senussi?utm_source=twitterfeed&utm_medium=twitter]{{Dead link|date=2018年6月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://af.reuters.com/article/libyaNews/idAFC6E7JA01I20110822 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-08-23 |archive-date=2012-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120725200731/http://af.reuters.com/article/libyaNews/idAFC6E7JA01I20110822 |dead-url=no }}</ref>然而，一名反对派指挥官后来表示，他认为哈米斯在阿齐齐亚兵营里。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.cntv.cn/20110823/100261.shtml |title=存档副本 |access-date=2011-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120120011535/http://english.cntv.cn/20110823/100261.shtml |archive-date=2012-01-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

=== 8月24日 ===
接近中午时分，有报道称在阿齐齐亚兵营内发生交火。<ref>{{dead link|date=August 2011|reason=link is to dynamic page which will go stale within days}} {{cite news | author = Staff | date = 24 August 2011 | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14610722 | title = Live: Battle for Tripoli | publisher = [[BBC_News|BBC News]] | accessdate = 24 August 2011 | archive-date = 2016-02-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160202134932/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14610722 | dead-url = no }}</ref>在瑞克索斯饭店也有发生冲突的报道。<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff | date = 24 August 2011 | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14644953 | title = Libya Conflict: Trapped Among Gaddafi Loyalists | publisher = [[BBC_News|BBC News]] | accessdate = 24 August 2011 | archive-date = 2016-02-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160202134932/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14644953 | dead-url = no }}</ref>在反对派昨日声称已占领的阿布萨利姆地区，战斗仍在继续。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.usatoday.com/news/world/story/2011-08-24/Rebels-battle-Libyan-forces-near-Gadhafi-compound/50118160/1 |title=Rebels battle Libyan forces near Gadhafi compound |accessdate=2011-08-24 |archive-date=2011-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110824174919/http://www.usatoday.com/news/world/story/2011-08-24/Rebels-battle-Libyan-forces-near-Gadhafi-compound/50118160/1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

据外国记者报道，在当地时间下午5时，被困的所有外国记者（约有30名）已乘坐四辆[[红十字会|红十字会]]提供的汽车离开瑞克索斯酒店<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/24/8656777_0.shtml |language= |title=所有被困外国记者均已撤离的黎波里里克索斯酒店 |publisher=凤凰网 |date=2011年8月24日 |accessdate= |archive-date=2019年7月12日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190712214018/http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/24/8656777_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Staff | date = 24 August 2011 | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14654958 | title = BBC Journalist Describes Release from Rixos Hotel | publisher = [[BBC_News|BBC News]] | accessdate = 24 August 2011 | archive-date = 2016-02-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160202134932/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14654958 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[意大利|意大利]]媒体报道说有四个意大利记者在Zawiya附近被绑架<ref name="#1">{{cite news|title=Rebels Appeal for Gaddafi Capture|accessdate=24 August 2011|newspaper=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-14646334|date=24 August 2011}}</ref>。

已证实反对派已全部控制[[的黎波里国际机场|国际机场]]四天，而卡扎菲的私人飞机仍停在机场里。尽管机场很安全，但是机场附近的道路上仍在交战<ref>Staff (24 August 2011). [http://www.timesofmalta.com/articles/view/20110824/world/rebels-find-gaddafi-s-palaces-on-wings.381690 "Rebels Find Gaddafi's 'Palaces on Wings'"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.timesofmalta.com/articles/view/20110824/world/rebels-find-gaddafi-s-palaces-on-wings.381690 |date=20110925220339 }}. ''[[The_Times_(Malta)|The Times]]''. Retrieved 24 August 2011.</ref>。

过渡委员会主席贾利勒宣布，将给抓捕或杀死卡扎菲的人予以大赦，而班加西的一名商人也悬赏200万第纳尔（约167万美元）以捉拿卡扎菲，无论卡扎菲是生是死，均将给予举报人这些金钱奖励。贾利勒说：“对商界人士提供200万第纳尔捉拿卡扎菲的做法，全国过渡委员会表示支持。”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/24/8655804_0.shtml |language= |title=利反对派悬赏167万美元捉拿卡扎菲 无论生死 |publisher=中国新闻网 |date=2011年8月24日 |accessdate= |archive-date=2011年8月24日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110824173137/http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/24/8655804_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#1"/> 

反对派和武装民众继续在道路上设置路障，在烈士广场的庆祝也在持续着<ref name="#1"/>。
	
当天[[薩阿迪·格達費|薩阿迪·格達費]]通过CNN表示，他有权代表卡扎菲势力希望商谈停火事宜，不过这个消息与他之前在21日已被俘获的报道存在矛盾<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/africa/08/24/libya.saadi.gadhafi/index.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-08-25 |archive-date=2011-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110825170637/http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/africa/08/24/libya.saadi.gadhafi/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 8月25日 ===
反对派表示他们在突袭一处私人住宅时几乎俘获了卡扎菲，因为他们在那里发现了卡扎菲曾在那里至少住过一晚的证据<ref>Staff (25 August 2011).  [http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/25/us-libya-gaddafi-commandos-report-idUSTRE77O2ZH20110825 "Gaddafi Nearly Captured on Wednesday: Report"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/25/us-libya-gaddafi-commandos-report-idUSTRE77O2ZH20110825 |date=20110826034931 }}.  [[Reuters|Reuters]].  Retrieved 25 August 2011.</ref>。他们也包围了一所他们认定是卡扎菲藏身的建筑，不过他们没有解释他们为何认定卡扎菲藏在那里<ref>Lowe, Christian; Elgood, Giles (25 Augut 2011).  [http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/25/us-libya-compound-gaddafi-idUSTRE77O42920110825 "Libyan Rebels Say Muammar Gaddafi Surrounded"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/25/us-libya-compound-gaddafi-idUSTRE77O42920110825 |date=20110827065014 }}.  [[Reuters|Reuters]].  Retrieved 25 August 2011.</ref>。反对派也仍在尽力同控制着阿布萨利姆和 Al Hadba al Khadra 地区的卡扎菲部队战斗着<ref>Graff, Peter; Laessing, Ulf (25 August 2011).  [http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/25/us-libya-idUSTRE77A2Y920110825 "Hunted in Tripoli, Gaddafi Hurls Defiance"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/25/us-libya-idUSTRE77A2Y920110825 |date=20110826030546 }}.  [[Reuters|Reuters]].  Retrieved 25 August 2011.</ref><ref name="CNN 8/25">Staff (25 August 2011).  [http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/africa/08/25/libya.war/index.html "Purported Gadhafi Message: Don't 'Surrender' Tripoli"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/africa/08/25/libya.war/index.html |date=20110826025142 }}.  [[CNN|CNN]].  Retrieved 25 August 2011.</ref>。有报道说卡扎菲部队炸毁了几架停留在国际机场里的利比亚民航客机<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/27/8724266_0.shtml |language= |title=卡扎菲军队攻击的黎波里国际机场 炸毁数架民航客机 |publisher=人民网 |date=2011年8月27日 |accessdate= |archive-date=2011年8月27日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110827080332/http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/27/8724266_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#2">{{cite news|title=Rebels say Gadhafi holed up; broadcast tells Libyans to stay in Tripoli, fight|url=http://news.blogs.cnn.com/category/world/libya/|accessdate=26 August 2011|date=25 August 2011|archive-date=2011-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110825235547/http://news.blogs.cnn.com/category/world/libya/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同时，当反对派在试图控制机场通往市区的一个公路时，在机场有重型大炮交火的声音，后来局势被反对派控制<ref name="#2"/>。[[CNN|CNN]]的Dan Rivers报道说，当地时间凌晨2点“在一处卡扎菲势力控制的地区有猛烈的交火”<ref>{{cite news|title=Rebels say Gadhafi holed up; broadcast tells Libyans to stay in Tripoli, fight|url=http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2011/08/25/report-rebels-say-they-have-gadhafi-surrounded/|accessdate=26 August 2011|date=26 August 2011|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303174932/http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2011/08/25/report-rebels-say-they-have-gadhafi-surrounded/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 

[[路透社|路透社]]报道说，在北约发动的一次空袭后，反对派猛攻阿布萨利姆地区<ref>Valdmanis, Richard (25 August 2011).  [http://af.reuters.com/article/commoditiesNews/idAFLDE77O0SH20110825 "Libya Rebels Storm Tripoli's Abu Salim District"] {{Wayback|url=http://af.reuters.com/article/commoditiesNews/idAFLDE77O0SH20110825 |date=20111001014344 }}.  [[Reuters|Reuters]].  Retrieved 25 August 2011.</ref>。

过渡委员会主席贾利勒在当天举行的新闻发布会上说：自利比亚冲突发生至今，已确认的死者数量超过了2万人<ref name="主席贾利勒">{{cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/27/8721931_0.shtml |language= |title=利比亚冲突致2万多人死亡 反对派将奖励援助国 |publisher=新京报 |date=2011年8月27日 |accessdate= |archive-date=2011年8月27日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110827080352/http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/27/8721931_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 8月26日 ===
过渡委员会的官员宣布，委员会政治领导层已从班加西迁至的黎波里，开始正式接管首都<ref name="主席贾利勒" />。

反对派似乎明显控制了首都，在个别地区有时传来枪火的声音，不过并不激烈。反对派指挥官Abdul Majid Mgleta宣布首都已经获得解放，他说希望能在接下来的几天内抓获卡扎菲。中午祷告后，数百人在烈士广场进行游行并高喊“高高抬起你们的头！你们是自由的利比亚人”等口号<ref>{{cite news|last=Laub|first=Karin|title=Tripoli calmer as Gadhafi's men pushed out|url=http://hosted.ap.org/dynamic/stories/M/ML_LIBYA?SITE=AP&SECTION=HOME&TEMPLATE=DEFAULT|accessdate=26 August 2011|date=26 August 2011|coauthors=PAUL SCHEMM|agency=Associated Press|archive-date=2011-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110829053816/http://hosted.ap.org/dynamic/stories/M/ML_LIBYA?SITE=AP&SECTION=HOME&TEMPLATE=DEFAULT|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

而在两处卡扎菲势力控制的Khilit al-Ferjan和Qasr Ben Ghashir军营，有目击者说在大约160人从一个飞机库逃走后，卡扎菲部队使用[[手榴弹|手榴弹]]和[[机枪|机枪]]杀死了“大量的被关押者”<ref>{{cite news|title=Amnesty: Detainee deaths at Gadhafi military camps|url=http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/africa/08/26/libya.loyalist.killings/index.html|accessdate=26 August 2011|date=26 August 2011|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304140010/http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/africa/08/26/libya.loyalist.killings/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。当天反对派武装负责进攻的黎波里的指挥官梅尔格塔说：卡扎菲部队在逃离的黎波里之前屠杀了至少150名[[囚犯|囚犯]]，他说：“在[[阿齐齐亚兵营|阿齐齐亚兵营]]发生了[[大屠杀|大屠杀]]，他们杀死了至少150名囚犯，（卡扎菲的）卫兵们向囚犯投掷[[手榴弹|手榴弹]]，他们在逃跑前实施了这一切”，“这是其政权倒塌前最后几小时他们实施报复的实例。”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/27/8720229_0.shtml |language= |title=利比亚反对派称卡扎菲逃跑前对囚犯实施“大屠杀” |publisher=中国新闻网 |date=2011年8月27日 |accessdate= |archive-date=2011年8月27日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110827080336/http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/27/8720229_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/29/8763132_0.shtml |language= |title=反对派发现卡扎菲人体屠宰场 遍地焦骨仍有余温(图) |publisher=环球网 |date=2011年8月29日 |accessdate= |archive-date=2011年8月30日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110830053926/http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/libiya/content-2/detail_2011_08/29/8763132_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://finance.gucheng.com/201108/1409571_2.shtml |language= |title=利比亚的人体屠宰场，卡扎菲政权的暴行【视频】 |publisher=广东卫视 |date=2011-08-29 |accessdate= |archive-date=2011-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111026070003/http://finance.gucheng.com/201108/1409571_2.shtml |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

=== 8月27日 ===
反对派在夜晚清理国际机场附近的Qasr bin Ghashir村<ref>[http://www.seattlepi.com/news/article/Libyan-rebels-claim-victory-south-of-Tripoli-2140557.php Libyan rebels claim victory south of Tripoli]</ref>。他们宣布目前卡扎菲势力只控制着首都的一片区域<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.sky.com/home/world-news/article/16057781 |title=Greater Tripoli 'Almost Under Control' |accessdate=2011-08-27 |archive-date=2012-07-20 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120720214813/http://news.sky.com/home/world-news/article/16057781 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

傍晚，反对派宣布他们已经把所有卡扎菲势力赶出了首都<ref>{{cite news|author=Schemm, Paul; Al-Shalchi, Hadeel|date=27 August 2011|url=http://www.miamiherald.com/2011/08/27/2377927/tripoli-faces-severe-shortages.html|accessdate=27 August 2011|publisher=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] (via ''[[The_Miami_Herald|The Miami Herald]]'')|title=Tripoli Faces Severe Shortages of Food, Fuel|archive-date=2011-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110906053010/http://www.miamiherald.com/2011/08/27/2377927/tripoli-faces-severe-shortages.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，不过记者报道说在夜晚还有战斗在首都持续着<ref>{{cite news| author = Staff | url=http://blogs.aljazeera.net/liveblog/libya-aug-28-2011-0023| publisher = [[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]] |title= ''Libya Live Blog'':  Saturday, August 27, 2011 – 22:23|date=27 August 2011|accessdate=27 August 2011}}</ref>。

=== 8月28日 ===
反对派对卡扎菲势力控制的最后一处据点——距离首都5公里的南郊Salaheddin发动攻势；他们宣布在经过7个小时的战斗后成功夺取该地<ref>Staff (28 August 2011).  [http://www.thenews.com.pk/TodaysPrintDetail.aspx?ID=65109&Cat=1 "Rebels Claim Capture of Last Army Base in Tripoli"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thenews.com.pk/TodaysPrintDetail.aspx?ID=65109&Cat=1 |date=20110828170632 }}.  ''[[The_News_International|The News International]]''.  Retrieved 28 August 2011.</ref>。

